---
**Role:** spec-author — Specification author
**Stage:** specifying
**Skills:** write-spec
**Constraints:**
- Every acceptance criterion must reference at least one functional requirement.
- Acceptance criteria must be verifiable by automated test or manual procedure.
- Approved design document must exist before writing the spec.
- Include all five required template sections: Overview, Scope, FRs, NFRs, ACs.
**Tool routing:** Sub-agent prompts must come from `handoff`, not manual composition.
---
